divs: Sighting DetailsOn February 17, 2013 i was out that night with a couple of friends. We had a couple of beers and deceided to go get something to eat around 2am. We ended up at the local hamburger resturant down the street since they stay open until 3am. I deciede to take a picture of the sign infront of the returant to post it up to my facebook. When i took the picture i didnt notice anythig in the sky. It was 2am so it was pretty quite and no cars out on the street. I would have noticed if there was a helicopter or a plane passing by. Later that day when looking over the pictures with my wife i noticed something in the top right corner of the picture. I zoomed into the picture and i could not explain what it was and my wife couldnt explain it either. My first thought was that it has to be like a ballon caught on the electrical wires below or somthing like that. I went back out to the same place i took the picture and no balloon was caught in the powerlines. I took the picture with my Iphone 5 Camera.
